# Cardoil Avantaj — Design System

You are responsible for maintaining visual consistency across this Next.js marketing site for **Cardoil Avantaj** (Romanian B2B transport & fuel broker).

The site uses the **Translo Home-2** theme as its primary UI layer, with **Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui** for forms and a few legacy inner-page blocks. Follow the rules below — do not mix patterns arbitrarily.

---

## Source of truth (read before styling)

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/styles/translo/main.scss` | Translo theme SCSS entry — modules, vendor CSS, Cardoil overrides |
| `src/styles/translo/abstracts/_variables.scss` | Brand tokens (`$thm-primary`, layout sizes) |
| `src/styles/translo/base/_brand.scss` | CSS custom properties scoped to `.homeTwo` |
| `src/styles/translo/components/` | Cardoil-specific overrides (hero, accordion, swiper) |
| `src/app/globals.css` | Tailwind tokens, shadcn theme, brand utilities for forms |
| `src/app/layout.tsx` | Root layout: `<html>`, global CSS imports, metadata |
| `src/app/(site)/layout.tsx` | Site shell: header, footer, smooth scroll, animations |
| `src/lib/content.ts` | Copy, nav, images, services, stats — not styling |
| `src/lib/pexels.ts` | Pexels fallback URLs when CDN/local images fail |
| `components.json` | shadcn/ui config (`base-nova`, Base UI) |

**Import order in root layout:** `globals.css` then Translo vendor CSS + `main.scss`.

**App Router:** All public pages live under `src/app/(site)/` (route group — URLs unchanged).

When changing brand green, update **`abstracts/_variables.scss`**, **`base/_brand.scss`**, and **`globals.css`** (`--brand`, `--ring`) together.

---

## Architecture overview

```
Primary (Translo Home-2)          Secondary (Tailwind / shadcn)
─────────────────────────         ─────────────────────────────
SiteHeader / SiteFooter           ContactForm (forms/)
SitePageHeader                    AboutAccordion, Partners (/despre)
home/* sections (hero, about…)    SiteImage on inner pages
Tailwind grid + .thm-btn          Card, Input, Accordion (ui/)
icomoon icons                     buttonVariants for form CTAs
Swiper sliders                    providers/ (Lenis, scroll animations)
```

**Rules:**
- New pages and sections → **Translo patterns** (`sec-title-two`, `.padding`, `.thm-btn`, `.container` + Tailwind grid)
- Do **not** add new files under removed legacy paths (`components/layout/`, `components/sections/`)
- Forms → `ContactForm` inside `.company-benefit-one__form` or equivalent Translo panel
- Copy and image URLs → `content.ts`; Pexels keys → `pexels.ts`

