## Typography

Translo loads **Rubik** (headings) and **Krub** (body) via `base/_fonts.scss`.

| Pattern | Use for |
|---------|---------|
| `.sec-title-two` + `.sub-title h5` | Section eyebrows |
| `.sec-title-two h2` | Section headings |
| `.thm-btn` + `.txt` | Primary CTAs |
| icomoon `<span className="icon-*" />` or `<i className="icon-*">` | Decorative / UI icons |

**Rules:**
- Prefer Translo title blocks over ad-hoc heading classes on themed pages
- Site language is Romanian (`lang="ro"`) — preserve diacritics
- Lucide icons only inside shadcn components, not Translo sections

---

## Layout & spacing

| Pattern | Use for |
|---------|---------|
| `.padding` | Default vertical section rhythm (Translo) |
| `.container` + Tailwind `grid` / `flex` | Layout — match existing pages (e.g. `grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2`) |
| `SitePageHeader` | Inner page hero (breadcrumb + title) |
| `.section` / `.container-page` | **Legacy Tailwind only** — `/despre` mixed blocks |

**Rules:**
- Inner pages: `SitePageHeader` then `<section className="… padding">` with `.container`
- Do not nest `.container` inside `.container`
- Reuse existing Translo section class names (`about-two`, `services-two`, `contact-one`) when extending pages

