## Swiper sliders

Used in hero, services carousel, testimonials, partner logos.

**Required config for custom nav buttons:**

```tsx
navigation={{
  nextEl: "#…-swiper-button-next",
  prevEl: "#…-swiper-button-prev",
  addIcons: false, // prevents Swiper 11 SVG from overlapping icomoon icons
}}
```

Nav buttons use `.swiper-nav-style1` + icomoon `icon-left-arrow-5` / `icon-right-arrow-5`. Style overrides live in `react-adjustment.css`.

Import in slider components: `swiper/css`, and `swiper/css/navigation` when Navigation module is used.

---

## shadcn/ui (forms & legacy sections)

| Component | Path | Notes |
|-----------|------|-------|
| `ContactForm` | `components/forms/contact-form.tsx` | `variant="dark"` on Translo dark panels |
| `Input`, `Textarea` | `components/ui/*` | All form fields |
| `Accordion` | `components/ui/accordion.tsx` | `/despre` about content |
| `Card` | `components/ui/card.tsx` | Legacy Tailwind panels only |

**Base UI note:** `Button` does not support `asChild`. Style links with `className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant: "brand" }))}`.

Add components via: `npx shadcn@latest add <component> -y`

