## Images

- **Primary CDN:** `cardoilavantaj.ro` via `content.ts`
- **Local theme assets:** `/img/…` (shapes, backgrounds from Translo)
- **Fallbacks:** `FallbackImage`, `FallbackBackground`, `SiteImage` with `fallbackKey` from `pexels.ts`
- Remote patterns in `next.config.ts`: `cardoilavantaj.ro`, `images.pexels.com`
- Meaningful `alt` text in Romanian; `sizes` on Next.js `Image`

Decorative icomoon icons: `aria-hidden="true"`.

---

## Accessibility

- One `<h1>` per page (usually inside hero or `TransloPageHeader` as `h2` — match Translo convention)
- Forms: `<label htmlFor="…">` on every field
- Testimonials: `<blockquote>` + `<cite>` where applicable
- Visible focus on shadcn controls — do not remove `focus-visible:ring-*`
- Color contrast: green `#00a44f` on white and white on dark backgrounds

---

## Responsive design

Translo handles breakpoints via `responsive.css` and Tailwind responsive utilities (`xl:grid-cols-2`, `lg:hidden`, etc.).

**Rules:**
- Follow existing Translo responsive patterns in module CSS before adding custom media queries
- Verify mobile menu, hero text, and swiper nav at narrow widths
- Swiper breakpoints already defined in slider components — mirror when adding new carousels

---

## Design evolution workflow

1. **Check** if a Translo module class or existing component covers the pattern
2. **Extend content** in `content.ts` for copy/images
3. **Add Translo section** under `components/translo/` if reusable
4. **Override CSS** in `react-adjustment.css` or `color-1.css` — never edit `style-main.css` directly unless extracting a patch
5. **Use Tailwind/shadcn** only for forms or isolated legacy blocks

---

## Review checklist

- [ ] Translo classes and `.thm-btn` for themed pages — not legacy `sections/*`
- [ ] Brand green via `--thm-primary` / `--brand`, no hardcoded hex
- [ ] Copy in `content.ts`, images with Pexels fallback where appropriate
- [ ] Swiper nav uses `addIcons: false` + icomoon icons
- [ ] `ContactForm` with correct `variant` on form pages
- [ ] Romanian copy with correct diacritics
- [ ] Responsive at mobile and desktop
- [ ] Accessibility: labels, focus, semantic headings

---

## Anti-patterns

```tsx
// ❌ Legacy header/footer on new pages
import { Header } from "@/components/layout/header";

// ❌ Tailwind page hero on Translo pages
<PageHero label="…" title="…" />

// ❌ Swiper without addIcons: false (double arrow icons)
navigation={{ nextEl: "#…", prevEl: "#…" }}

// ❌ Hardcoded brand color in Translo section
style={{ color: "#00a44f" }}

// ❌ Radix asChild on Base UI Button
<Button asChild><Link href="…">…</Link></Button>
```

```tsx
// ✅ Translo inner page
<TransloPageHeader title="Servicii" />
<section className="services-two padding">
  <div className="container">…</div>
</section>

// ✅ Translo CTA
<Link className="thm-btn" href="/oferta">
  <span className="txt">Solicită ofertă</span>
  <i className="icon-right-arrow" />
</Link>

// ✅ Image with fallback
<SiteImage src={aboutImages.team} alt="…" fallbackKey="team" />

// ✅ Form on dark panel
<ContactForm variant="dark" />
```
